DOORBELL RINGS

41:43.580 --> 41:45.020
CHATTER FROM RADIO
IN BACKGROUND

41:45.180 --> 41:46.220
Mum?!

41:48.140 --> 41:49.780
Mum?

41:51.620 --> 41:54.460
FOOTSTEPS THUD ON STAIRS

41:57.260 --> 41:59.180
Mum?

42:01.780 --> 42:03.740
Wake up, Mum.

42:05.940 --> 42:07.380
Jess...

42:08.700 --> 42:09.940
Jessie, what is it?

42:11.620 --> 42:14.540
When Hayley broke her arm that time
when we were on holiday,

42:14.700 --> 42:16.060
did she have a plate fitted?

42:16.220 --> 42:17.380
What?

42:17.580 --> 42:19.780
I think we were in Cyprus.
Did she have a plate fitted?

42:19.940 --> 42:21.380
Why?

42:21.540 --> 42:22.700
Did she?

42:24.380 --> 42:25.500
Yes.

42:27.180 --> 42:29.020
It was a compound fracture.

42:29.220 --> 42:31.700
She had it done
at the local hospital.

42:31.860 --> 42:32.940
Why?

42:33.100 --> 42:35.780
You're gonna have to get up, Mum.

42:35.980 --> 42:38.620
The police are gonna be
coming down from London.

42:43.100 --> 42:45.420
They think they've found her.

42:45.580 --> 42:47.020
They think they've found Hayley.

42:56.100 --> 42:58.900
APPROACHING FOOTSTEPS

43:08.020 --> 43:09.420
Eliot?

43:17.580 --> 43:18.900
Hey, Els, how you doing?

43:20.980 --> 43:22.220
Hi, Dad.

43:28.580 --> 43:31.420
GULLS CALL

43:59.340 --> 44:06.420
Eliot!

44:14.900 --> 44:17.540
My client's mother, Mrs Avery,

44:17.740 --> 44:20.420
was diagnosed with dementia
over seven years ago.

44:20.580 --> 44:22.300
As you can imagine...

44:22.460 --> 44:23.740
Oh, shit!

44:48.980 --> 44:52.140
BREATHES HEAVILY

44:59.940 --> 45:03.140
Yes, she had a plate fitted,

45:03.300 --> 45:05.660
and it was in Cyprus.

45:12.540 --> 45:13.780
It's her.

